:false,"overview":"Singleton Kartar Singh is left with the responsibility of raising his two orphaned nephews. He asks his brother in Punjab to raise Charan and his sister in London to raise Karan. When the twins cross continents, they leave behind a trail of confusion.","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":0.324,"vote_count":44,"poster_path":"/cSqLPtE4fkn2wrpxlw5xXraHDNH.jpg","release_date":"2017-07-28","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/dXhMRqk2cY2miQFVou6sxWkjysM.jpg","original_title":"मुबारकां","original_language":"hi"},{"id":271484,"adult":false,"title":"Beti No. 1","video":false,"overview":"This warmhearted comedy takes place in a household completely dominated by Durga Bhatnagar, an imposing matriarch who's desperate for a grandson and heir.","genre_ids":[35,18,10751,10749],"popularity":0.1928,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/klAxXAuVmsPHaoTCwFQ0vLqAikb.jpg","release_date":"2000-11-10","vote_average":3.5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Beti No. 1","original_language":"hi"},{"id":1252457,"adult":false,"title":"Vijay 69","video":false,"overview":"An adventurous, foul-mouthed former swimming coach reaches for record-breaking glory when he attempts a triathlon at 69 years old.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":0.4176,"vote_count":27,"poster_path":"/tSQzRaYyKEjM8gEyhqayU4rhbdU.jpg","release_date":"2024-11-08","vote_average":6.87,"backdrop_path":"/oU9WaOwdaxmO6HDKKVf5O3GnrO2.jpg","original_title":"विजय 69","original_language":"hi"},{"id":1682,"adult":false,"title":"Mothra vs. Godzilla","video":false,"overview":"Journalists Ichiro Sakai and Junko cover the wreckage of a typhoon when an enormous egg is found and claimed by greedy entrepreneurs. Mothra's fairies arrive and are aided by the journalists in a plea for its return. As their requests are denied, Godzilla arises near Nagoya and the people of Infant Island must decide if they are willing to answer Japan's own pleas for help.","genre_ids":[18,28,878],"popularity":1.7848,"vote_count":326,"poster_path":"/y49v