i to locate him. Gopi accepts this assignment and must battle women, venomous snakes, gangsters, kidnappers, a robot-human, as well as Priya Varma - who believes that he killed her father, Dr Varma, Neelam - who is determined to seduce and then enslave him, and the unknown and mysterious head of an organization simply known as S.S.O.","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":0.1509,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/x1ZNu4MuCfub9q8Kxrm24RoNmJx.jpg","release_date":"1979-07-22","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":"/ydO2smk93gfgVR6k58EokKutO7C.jpg","original_title":"Surakksha","original_language":"hi"},{"id":1870,"adult":false,"title":"Fantomas Unleashed","video":false,"overview":"In the second episode of the trilogy Fantômas kidnaps distinguished scientist professor Marchand with the aim to develop a super weapon that will enable him to menace the world. Fantômas is also planning to abduct a second scientist, professor Lefebvre.","genre_ids":[35,80,12,14],"popularity":1.4684,"vote_count":561,"poster_path":"/wtMGO5JyORkd1CF7e6pyn47dITm.jpg","release_date":"1965-12-08","vote_average":6.726,"backdrop_path":"/2m4oXN0EitDYsHpVoPOXNhChk7s.jpg","original_title":"Fantômas se déchaîne","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1875,"adult":false,"title":"Fantomas vs. Scotland Yard","video":false,"overview":"In the third and final episode of the trilogy, Fantômas imposes a head tax on the rich, threatening to kill those who do not comply.","genre_ids":[35,80,12,14],"popularity":2.021,"vote_count":560,"poster_path":"/wrs0leNyQwVbUOoXCnfMf3Bix4V.jpg","release_date":"1967-03-16","vote_average":6.723,"backdrop_path":"/6BMk2AnieC5sDkhcBiNjWWoxvHe.jpg","original_title":"Fantômas contre Scotland Yard","original_language":"fr"},{"id":273166,"adult":false,"title":"O Teri","video":false,"overview":"Prantabh and Anand, associated with a news channel in Delhi, are in search of a big scam to prove a point to their senior. A dead body accidentally lands up in their car.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":0.3446,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/8yDmeoOKcWtp0TU9n66hAfVAqy3.jpg","release_date":"2014-03-28","vote_average":2.2,"backdrop_path":"/qSeMx4F9dqinXuNqlg1QNBMuKzy.jpg","original_title":"ओ तेरी","original_language":"hi"},{"id":465634,"adult":false,"title":"Sindoor","video":false,"overview":"Laxmi is half of a famous singing couple when both her relationship and career are destroyed by the jealous plotting of her husband , Vijay. Years later, Laxmi is widowed and raising a stepdaughter, Lalita, when Vijay returns to the scene to meddle in her new family's affairs and once again threaten her domestic happiness.","genre_ids":[10751,18],"popularity":0.3612,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/1yTKMQaz1LHeQbJhzs17H8bRYj5.jpg","release_date":"1987-07-31","vote_average":3.5,"backdrop_path":"/5llxS1Lz4J5gLE40sDUZUW6yyZ9.jpg","original_title":"Sindoor","original_language":"hi"},{"id":465641,"adult":false,"title":"Massey Sahib","video":false,"overview":"In a small, tribal district town of Central India in 1929, Francis Massey is the 'English Type Babu' at the Deputy Commissioner's office. Massey believes that because he is Christian and can speak English, he is a cut above other Indians and not very different from the white sahibs he serves. For a man of lowly birth, Massey has risen to a dizzying height. On the other hand, he acknowledges no realistic limits to his own free spirit. Whenever the real world fails him, he improvises - boldly, imaginatively. Alas, the unsmiling, implacable machinery of the Raj has no room for Massey Sahib, the travelling salesman, road foreman and entertainer. Right up to the bitter end, Massey believes that Deputy Commissioner Adam Sahib will step in and save him.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.1369,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/oFqhcrngrwD3QZD634ZBqcneXiD.jpg","release_date":"1986-04-29","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Massey Sahib","original_language":"hi"},{"id":465642,"adult":false,"title":"Parmanu: The Story of Pokhran","video":